(135, 1, '2021-05-16 15:24:58', '2021-05-16 12:24:58', '<h6>CYCLES</h6>		\n															<img width=\"2560\" height=\"1709\" src=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-scaled.jpg 2560w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-1024x684.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-768x513.jpg 768w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/three-pupils-of-primary-school-go-hand-in-hand-boy-and-girl-with-school-bags-behind-the-back-beginning-of-school-lessons-warm-day-of-fall-back-to-school-little-first-graders1-2048x1367.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />															\n			<h4>Nos Cycles</h4>		\n		<p>Le Groupe Scolaire Shahd accueille les enfants de la maternelle (toute petite section à partir de l\'âge de 2 ans, puis en petite section, moyenne section et grande section, en primaire, au collège et au lycée. Au sortir de la maternelle, les enfants intègrent le cycle primaire. Ainsi nos élèves peuvent suivre tout leur cursus scolaire dans notre école jusqu\'à la re année. L\'entrée au collège puis au lycée est entériné par un examen interne qui valider le passage au cycle supérieur. Ils ont la possibilité de bénéficier, dès leur plus jeune âge, de toutes les infrastructures mises à leur disposition, d\'un suivi plus individualisé grâce à la concertation professorale inter cycles et d\'une continuité dans les pratiques et méthodes pédagogiques pratiquées au sein de notre établissement. </p>', 'Cycles', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cycles', '', '', '2021-05-16 23:02:14', '2021-05-16 20:02:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/PFE/?page_id=135', 0, 'page', '', 0),
