tissage tout au long de la vie.</h2>		\n			<figure><img width=\"383\" height=\"249\" src=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/1.jpg 383w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/1-300x195.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 383px) 100vw, 383px\" /></figure><h3>Veiller au bien-etre et à l\'épanouissement</h3>		\n			<figure><img width=\"381\" height=\"245\" src=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/2.jpg 381w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/2-300x193.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 381px) 100vw, 381px\" /></figure><h3>Favorriser l\'autonomie</h3>		\n			<figure><img width=\"385\" height=\"248\" src=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3.jpg 385w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/3-300x193.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 385px) 100vw, 385px\" /></figure><h3>le développement des compétences</h3>		\n			<figure><img width=\"383\" height=\"249\" src=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/1.jpg 383w, http://localhost/PFE/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/1-300x195.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 383px) 100vw, 383px\" /></figure><h3>sensibiliser aux responsabilités sociales</h3>', 'Maternelle', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '132-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-18 15:02:53', '2021-05-18 12:02:53', '', 132, 'http://localhost/PFE/?p=245', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
